<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA8">
<l>āyiṉē ṉāḷvāṉuk kaṉṟē peṟaṟkariya</l>
<l>ṉāyiṉē ṉaḵtaṉṟē yāmāṟu - tūya</l>
<l>puṉaṟkaṅkai yēṟṟāṉōr poṉvaraiyē pōlvā</l>
<l>ṉaṉaṟkaṅkai yēṟṟā ṉaruḷ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have become [servant] to the ruler that day. To him difficult to attain</l>
<l>I became [servant]. That, isn’t it, is the way it is, by the grace of him</l>
<l>who holds the Gaṅgā with pure floods, who is like a golden mountain,</l>
<l>who holds up his palm for fire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
